<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><b>Due to data protection regulations, I am unable to supply any details relating to another customer</b>. <br><br>Please <b>confirm the name and email address of the person you referred and I will investigate</b> on your behalf and get back to you with any information I can.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Please be advised that <b>once your friend has purchased, vouchers are not sent until 28 days after their policy start date</b>.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">In some circumstances, we may have received your friend's details from another source before your own referral. In this case, the referral is attributed to the initial source, and therefore the refer a friend offer does not apply.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">If your friend would like to contact us directly, we will happily discuss the details of their policy with them.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to get in touch.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Customer Service Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">T: 01242 808 740</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>